description: Two Car Garage & Private Roof Deck!  On the west side of South Boston, this penthouse offers spectacular views, an abundance of natural light, and a rare private two car garage. Corner placement and oversized windows flood every room with sunlight. Step outside to your own private roof deck—a true urban sanctuary, perfect for relaxing or entertaining under the open sky. Enjoy being just two blocks from the Broadway T station, shops, dining and all that South Boston has to offer. The open floor plan encompasses the living, kitchen and dining areas and opens to a balcony for additional outdoor enjoyment. The spacious layout includes an oversized primary bedroom (with wall of closets), a second bedroom and in-unit washer/dryer. Newly refinished hardwood floors and fresh paint throughout, plus a new fridge and furnace in 2025! If you are looking for breathtaking views, tons of natural light, secure parking, and exclusive outdoor space, this unit is a must see.
